data.title: Saint Peter's Church
data.meta_description: Saint Peter's Church is an Anglican Church Congregation located in North Mount Pleasant, South Carolina.
data.text:
JOIN US ONLINE OR IN-PERSON SUNDAYS AT 9:15 OR 11:00AM

During this time we are offering two in-person services each Sunday. We also provide online services that can be accessed during our regular worship service times or anytime on our YouTube channel. Our hope is that you will join us either in-person or online and begin to connect with our community that is centered around the life and teachings of Jesus Christ.

ONLINE LINKS

We are live streaming our in-person Sunday Worship Services at 9:15 and 11:00am. Use the “Sundays LIVE” image below to join us for worship during those times. Each service will then be uploaded to our YouTube channel, and our Saint Peter's app, early the following week and can be viewed through the “Watch Previous” link below.
